--- title: deeptool keywords: fastai sidebar: home_sidebar summary: "Tool for applying several deep learning methods on the MRNet dataset." ---

Current implementations:

  • DIAGNOSIS (MRNet based)

  • DCGAN

  • VQVAE - VQVAE2
  • INTROVAE

Install - not yet available¶

Later this will simply be:

pip install deeptool

For now the source code needs to be downloaded. Then navigation to the downloaded folder is required and the package can be installed with:

pip install -e .

How to use¶

from deeptool import *

# add some nice functionality here ;)
